snippet.title: Igor: The Game (Wii) - Playthrough / Longplay - (1080p, original console)
snippet.description:
Igor: The Game (Wii) Full Game Playthrough / Longplay / Walkthrough.
Played on a original Nintendo Wii console, recorded with Elgato Game Capture HD and upscaled to 1080p.

► Igor: The Game All Bosses video: https://youtu.be/97zeYOzFEgk

Genre: Action-adventure

Developer: Santa Cruz Games
Publisher: NA: SouthPeak Games, EU: Deep Silver

This game is also on Windows PC.

► Longplay and Playthrough playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLljauD_hVEDICYJJszrZTv0qEPIZtqwAc

► Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/10minGameplay

#IgorTheGame #playthrough #longplay
